{"tid":829773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來芝麻街真係gay","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T06:32:47.000Z","uid":59328,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"440decfbfd98017a4ce12b02ae63dc8a2f185648","tid":829773,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/237695/%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%A8%E5%8A%87%E8%AA%8Dbert-ernie%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6-%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E8%A1%97-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F237695%2F%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E5%258A%2587%25E8%25AA%258Dbert-ernie%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E4%25BE%25B6-%25E8%258A%259D%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B&d=h7tbDmTK8csxJeeCU%2Bz0FbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1fa97e38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/237695/%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%A8%E5%8A%87%E8%AA%8Dbert-ernie%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6-%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E8%A1%97-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n前編劇認Bert &amp; Ernie是同性伴侶　《芝麻街》否認：係好朋友！<br />\n<br />\n美國經典兒童節目《芝麻街》（Sesame Street）由1969年首播至今，已經有49年，除了陪伴全球兒童快樂地成長，更榮獲150多次艾美獎。節目中的經典角色，包括Big Bird、Elmo、Cookie Monster等，都深受兒童歡迎，而其中Bert同Ernie一直被傳是同性戀情侶（Gay Couple）這個話題，更成為大批網民的討論話題。<br />\n<br />\n據外國傳媒報道，《芝麻街》的前編劇Mark Saltzman日前受訪時曾透露過，Bert跟Ernie這對「好朋友」故事的靈感是建基於自己跟剪接師Arnold Glassman的關係，這對角色的設定是「恩愛的情侶」。這個消息發放後，隨即引來熱烈討論。不少網民都為Bert與Ernie「出櫃」此而高興。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今日「芝麻街工作室」（Sesame Workshop）其後發出聲明表示，Bert跟Ernie是沒有性取向的，他們型態上雖然看似人類，但其實他們只是布偶：「《芝麻街》一直堅持包容和接受，這是一個歡迎所有文化和背景的地方。 創造Bert和Ernie這兩個角色的設定是好朋友，希望從而教育小朋友，大家可以與那些跟自己截然不同的人相處。」<br />\n<br />\n當發出聲明後，Mark Saltzman到現在暫時還未有回應，那究竟Bert與Ernie這兩個角色是否真的是同性伴侶？ 1969年「創造」（演繹）Bert這個角色的資深演員Frank Oz指，「我知道他是誰、他是甚麼，不，他不是同性戀者！」（I know what and who he is. And no, he isn't gay.），後來再於twitter發帖寫道：「當有人問Mark Saltzman究竟Bert &amp; Ernie是否同性戀者，『他覺得是』並無問題，但他們（Bert &amp; Ernie）當然不是同志！」<br />\n<br />\n香港已經有反同組織屌緊芝麻街啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd50389f1ad54812d71658e9a455059e4e04fbb","tid":829773,"uid":32765,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"屌以為講緊蔣介石個戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"3ca5b04c87ed536c8da45ed2e183e8393fcd6e82","tid":829773,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd50389f1ad54812d71658e9a455059e4e04fbb","tid":829773,"uid":32765,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"屌以為講緊蔣介石個戇鳩仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"邊個蔣介石?"},{"pid":"5054af2b3c4f4df82c4545054691ebb0b2e44963","tid":829773,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"感覺上果個年代真係開放d, 包容d<br />\n反而現今資訊爆炸既年代仲保守<br />\n觀念保守既人更容易係多種渠道發表(<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">連登仔</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n呢個代邊有細佬睇芝麻街<br />\n講唔講出黎無影響<br />\n睇過都差唔多半百歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9687b061de9ddd566a3f626bed1e0ff8d83d60de","tid":829773,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5054af2b3c4f4df82c4545054691ebb0b2e44963","tid":829773,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"感覺上果個年代真係開放d, 包容d<br />\n反而現今資訊爆炸既年代仲保守<br />\n觀念保守既人更容易係多種渠道發表(<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">連登仔</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n呢個代邊有細佬睇芝麻街<br />\n講唔講出黎無影響<br />\n睇過都差唔多半百歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji